snippet.title: Reloader: test_subject - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Reloader: test_subject is a side-scroller shoot 'em up that claim to be "bullet-counting reload action" game, inspired by numerous masterpiece gun action movies and indie game 'Receiver'.

Become the Reloader who has the amazing gun shooting skill but no knowledge about the gun mechanisms, experience both realistic gun maneuvering and movie-like gun action.

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1706210/Reloader_test_subject/
